{"tid":860182,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[HXH] 有冇人好鍾意窩金?","createTime":"2018-10-13T06:52:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T08:53:55.000Z","uid":35644,"like":4,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"1c7feddcbfde0d802a869dba2072aeeeeeed178b","tid":860182,"uid":35644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T06:52:11.000Z","msg":"成套漫畫我最鍾意就係窩金 真係好撚型 佢打陰獸個part真係J撚到出血<br />\n可惜咁快就死左 好想睇佢屌打螞蟻<br />\n有時會諗 如果佢同鎖鍊佬打之前 冇俾陰獸整傷的話 會唔會冇咁快死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"659f2e50936843fad1e17d06d328fe7ebd4a8398","tid":860182,"uid":79355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T07:07:24.000Z","msg":"傷乜鳩 都吸番d毒出黎<br />\nD蟲又痾緊<br />\n<br />\n佢自己大意輸比個新手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18ca581225d8088e49c5cce4b0f13aaf060307bf","tid":860182,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"659f2e50936843fad1e17d06d328fe7ebd4a8398","tid":860182,"uid":79355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T07:07:24.000Z","msg":"傷乜鳩 都吸番d毒出黎<br />\nD蟲又痾緊<br />\n<br />\n佢自己大意輸比個新手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T07:18:40.000Z","msg":"主要係因為強化系嘅人通常都唔經大腦同唔用腦，你睇吓小岡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 然後再睇埋信長，居然傻到俾兩個細路呃到都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而具現化系係比較神經質，比較執著同完美主義，所以古拿比加出擊之前都已經度過晒諗過晒點對付佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但尚方只係用返平時嘅戰鬥模式，唔係針對古拿比加嘅做法應對，所以最後先輸"},{"pid":"a6de32f4b4fc71419ca157e39626b338a472a39e","tid":860182,"uid":11055,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T07:21:09.000Z","msg":"準備好譯名互屌大戰"},{"pid":"9b429745f5256c832f13dee40dc77265e0606ee4","tid":860182,"uid":34293,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T07:22:48.000Z","msg":"胡步勁"},{"pid":"b4c4731ce81ce5660949860378f12f419768a